      "created_at": "2023-05-12T08:23:41.443Z",
      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/bd21cfab2619ba7d3b1a82b93264d1c537bc22ef.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/bd21cfab2619ba7d3b1a82b93264d1c537bc22ef\" title=\"Screenshot_20230415-135552\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bd21cfab2619ba7d3b1a82b93264d1c537bc22ef_2_230x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_20230415-135552\" data-base62-sha1=\"qZ8GhWGEeQcWIgjMsUgWE9sjJlt\" width=\"230\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bd21cfab2619ba7d3b1a82b93264d1c537bc22ef_2_230x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bd21cfab2619ba7d3b1a82b93264d1c537bc22ef_2_345x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bd21cfab2619ba7d3b1a82b93264d1c537bc22ef_2_460x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bd21cfab2619ba7d3b1a82b93264d1c537bc22ef_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_20230415-135552</span><span class=\"informations\">1080\u00d72340 225 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\nHello<br>\nAs you can see on the attached screenshot, when I\u2019ve used split screen feature font was not really resized and It affects readability.</p>",
