      "id": 25782,
      "name": "",
      "username": "Alex",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2023-05-12T12:16:30.250Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi, we never designed split screen to be used on phones.  We never even imagined anyone would try this <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\">  It\u2019s interesting for sure.</p>\n<p>We did the bare minimum to get it working on tablets.  We are obviously very low cost and also not big like the leaders in the field but growing quickly. I say this because I want to be 100% transparent that we can add this to our list but since this is the first request for this it is less likely to get prioritized very soon.</p>\n<p>Sorry I don\u2019t have a better answer but being on small budgets we have to be careful what we work on and when.  We have to focus on critical stuff first.</p>",
