      "id": 25788,
      "name": "pietryna123",
      "username": "pietryna123",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecd19e/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2023-05-12T13:17:31.452Z",
      "cooked": "<p>As I\u2019m one of the few people who does not want and need to involve whole social part of working out I use bare phone as controller. Space limitation prevents me from using PC on stand (and it will cripple air flow of a vent <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/smiley.png?v=9\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smiley:\"> ) in front but sometims it\u2019s nice to watch something.</p>\n<p>Anyway I\u2019m not into mobile or frontend development but shouldnt it be just scaling issue? Because it looks like font size is not changing at all. Just chart is moving to the side, and table with tiles resize.</p>\n<p>I\u2019ve seen similar problem on some tablet but it was not about split screen directly but general ourcome looked the same. Font was not resized correctly.</p>",
