      "id": 25794,
      "name": "",
      "username": "Alex",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2023-05-12T14:57:02.535Z",
      "cooked": "<p>We don\u2019t scale fonts or use any auto-scaling so that has the potential to introduce new issues and when we have 50\u00b1 different device sizes, the complications that can come up are surprising.  I bet if I asked my developer he would say 3-hours to fix it and then he would spend 2-days fixing the unexpected side effects.  It frequently happens I ask for something that seems small and it gets big fast.  I am a developer too but not doing this work.</p>\n<p>Any, I love happy customers more than anything else so it is really hard for me to say this is going to have to wait but anything I see that is for one person that has potential side effects I have to be careful about and prioritize correctly.  It\u2019s never 1 person but one voice and a small number of silent people.  I hope you understand.  I guess tablet would be better but then you need a tablet bike mount\u2026</p>",
